Source: mongo-fdw
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), postgresql-server-dev-all (>= 217~), libmongoc-dev, libbson-dev, libjson-c-dev, pkgconf | pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.7.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/EnterpriseDB/mongo_fdw

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-mongo-fdw
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-mongo-fdw
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Breaks: ${postgresql:Breaks}
Description: MongoDB Foreign Data Wrapper for PostgreSQL
 This PostgreSQL extension implements a Foreign Data Wrapper (FDW) for MongoDB.
 .
  * Write-able FDW
  * Connection Pooling
  * JOIN push-down
  * AGGREGATE push-down
  * ORDER BY push-down
  * LIMIT OFFSET push-down
